Howdy!<br />
Welcome to my happy place.<br />
Mind the mutagenic sludge, and please don't feed the machinery.<br />
Oh, and holler if you see a big toothy cyborg thing covered in runes&#8230;<br />
always knows when it's bath time somehow.
<p>By the way, if you like what you see and want to enable me to make more of it, <a href="https://ko-fi.com/O5O8B7IA">I have a tip jar over on ko-fi! :3</a> <span style="text-decoration: blink;">█</span></p>
