<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Back&nbsp;on&nbsp;your&nbsp;feet.&nbsp;Your&nbsp;shift&nbsp;isn't&nbsp;over&nbsp;yet.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div style="font-size: 10pt; border: solid 3px #3A1713; font-family: verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: normal; padding: 0px 20px;">
<p><em>Data recovered from comm network black box, former Site 68</em><br />
<strong>Agent Farlow:</strong> <em>Uh, HQ? Doing my rounds down here on the Production floor, and I think some of the machinery just started back up.</em><br />
<strong>Assistant Director of Security Phillips</strong>: <em>Agent, I'm not sure I copy, please repeat?</em><br />
<strong>Agent Farlow:</strong> <em>This is Agent Farlow, patrolling the Production floor. I</em> definitely <em>have operational machiner-</em><br />
[distant clatter, followed by rapid series of modulating tones]<br />
<strong>Agent Farlow:</strong> <em>&#8230;the hell?</em><br />
<strong>ADS Phillips:</strong> <em>Report, agent. Whats going on down there?</em><br />
<strong>Agent Farlow:</strong> <em>HQ, I've got movement down here. Other than the machinery, that is. Think we've got intruders; moving in to check it out.</em><br />
<strong>ADS Phillips:</strong> <em>Recon only. Do not confront. I'll send some backup your way.</em><br />
[Sounds of rapid heavy impacts on metal interspersed with rapidly modulated tones]<br />
<strong>Agent Farlow:</strong> <em>Shit. Might be looking at a raid here&#8230; like CotBG or something, 'cause I don't think these guys are human. Pretty sure one of 'em just cleared a twenty foot gap in the catwalks.</em><br />
<strong>ADS Phillips:</strong> <em>Agent, withdraw to the stairwell and wait for backup.</em><br />
<strong>Agent Farlow:</strong> <em>Just a sec- one of 'ems holding still. Doing something with one of the control banks. Think I can get a better look&#8230;</em><br />
[Nearby heavy impact followed by sustained high pitched squeal]<br />
<strong>Agent Farlow:</strong> <em>Confirming non-human.</em><br />
[sustained high pitch squeal interspersed with screaming and rapid modulating tones]</p>
</div>
<br />
<a href="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP-748-5.jpg"><img src="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP-748-5.jpg" height="700px" alt="SCP-748-5.jpg" class="image" /></a></div>
</div>
