<div class="collapsible-block-content"><a href="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP-1507.jpg"><img src="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP-1507.jpg" alt="SCP-1507.jpg" class="image" /></a><br />
