<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Superfast&nbsp;(evolution)&nbsp;Jellyfish</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><a href="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP%201585%20vingettes.png"><img src="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP%201585%20vingettes.png" alt="SCP%201585%20vingettes.png" class="image" /></a></div>
<p>Its kind of weird, working on the aerial view made me realize both how small and how freaking huge <a href="/scp-1585">SCP-1585</a> is. It'd be hard to get lost on it, but there's plenty of room for a whole bunch of critters. Its bigger than some of the inhabited islands of Micronesia.</p>
