<div class="amberscreen">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP-1802&nbsp;(''Skip'')</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Skip&nbsp;is&nbsp;freaking&nbsp;adorable&nbsp;and&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;taking&nbsp;him&nbsp;home&nbsp;with&nbsp;me.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
