<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">CACK!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">Went through a bunch of brainstorming sketches for this one, trying to find an idea that really captured the little guy's vibe. And then it hit me while I was trawling google for pictures of corkcrakes: Audobon.<br />
<a href="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP-2337.jpg"><img src="http://visual-records.wdfiles.com/local--files/scps/SCP-2337.jpg" alt="SCP-2337.jpg" class="image" /></a><br />
Crex Crex Conclamani: The Cacophonic Corn Crake</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="amberscreen">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SCP-2490&nbsp;(Chaos&nbsp;Insurgency&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Operative&nbsp;Alpha-19)</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I&nbsp;didn't&nbsp;think&nbsp;this&nbsp;thing&nbsp;was&nbsp;all&nbsp;that&nbsp;scary&nbsp;when&nbsp;I&nbsp;started&nbsp;painting.</a></div>
