<p>So far we have Mecha-nobody, the black queen, monkey!Bright, Dr. Gerald, <a href="/scp-2006-j">SCP-2006-j</a>, Kondraki with <a href="/scp-682">SCP-682</a> and <a href="/scp-408">SCP-408</a>, Dr. Gears (I decided he's a cyborg in this 'verse), <a href="/scp-040">SCP-040</a>, <a href="/scp-079">Able</a>, and Pretty Magic Gaiden Mecha Tokyo-Mon Demon Ninja Sailor Clef himself in all his disquieting glory.</p>
<p>The list of characters I'm working on adding or have already added on the version on my harddrive includes:<br />
