<p>I'm actively looking for suggestions on who and what else needs to be in the full version: I'm looking to fill up the whole page ala one of those anime posters with everyone that's ever been on the show on them. (Leave suggestions <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-1281417/scorpion451-s-scp-art#post-2681159">here</a> if you have them!)</p>
